ráng du - 壯遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Minh-T%C3%B4ng/T%E1%BB%A9-thi%E1%BA%BFu-b%E1%BA%A3o-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-S%C3%B9ng-Thao/poem-oGxIQaP50ryYbR2GVVt1eA">Tứ thiếu bảo Trần Sùng Thao - 賜少保陳崇韜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Minh-T%C3%B4ng/author-4trx3YJ-cefKhX0g_XM7Sw">Trần Minh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/T%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-li%C3%AAn-c%C3%BA-ng%C5%A9-ng%C3%B4n-b%C3%A0i-lu%E1%BA%ADt-nh%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BB%A7-h%E1%BA%A1n-nh%E1%BB%8B-ti%C3%AAu-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-wMQlYGlF6aUupM2pBicmdQ">Tức cảnh liên cú ngũ ngôn bài luật nhất thủ, hạn “nhị tiêu” vận - 即景聯句五言排律一首，限二蕭韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Nh%C3%A2n-B%C3%ADch/Xu%C3%A2n-tuy%E1%BA%BFt/poem-rMq3RhY4BSPSuM0GrV3AQQ">Xuân tuyết - 春雪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Nh%C3%A2n-B%C3%ADch/author-G0aWOVa-5zyXpwAXdh6h3g">Ngô Nhân Bích</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
